Class ProjectModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.AbstractListModel<Project>
      • edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.modules.PlanningPoker.models.ProjectModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.ListModel<Project>

    public class ProjectModel
extends javax.swing.AbstractListModel<Project>
    List of projects pulled from the server. Add methods only add projects to the local instance, as the projects already exist on the server.
